  "elapsed_s": 103.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "One thing I should mention that I didn't mention before was that meanwhile-- during this period happened one very important event in my life, very, very important event of one-- [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] major importance.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "During my studies and, and stay and work in Italy, I made it at the competitions.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I was able to make other competitions, which I win again prizes, high prizes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "One was one competition in Italy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I win there the first price of the Accademia Chigiana in Italy.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then, very soon after that, I win the special prize of George Enescu International Competition in Romania.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] At the time, I was still citizen of Israel-- Israeli citizen.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] What happened was that I was accepted because they make a selection of whom they are able to accept for these auditions.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I was accepted as only one representative of, meanwhile, the new state of Israel.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I was the only one violinist competing of Israeli-- the new Israeli State.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Of course, in the beginning, nobody didn't know that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But soon as-- after that first round was over-- because they two rounds-- selective rounds, in which they, after that, select the first prize, second, third, fourth, and-- et cetera.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "My name started to appear in the newspapers there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And here immediately come in clear lights that there is one Israeli musician competitor in this.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And especially after the second circle-- second tour, when I was selected for the finals, so the semi-finals, again the name of Israel was there, showing up.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I start to receive tremendous amount of phones in my hotels.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
